{"tid":1155784,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"揀得殘體預咗俾人屌啦","createTime":"2019-05-15T07:28:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T10:08:29.000Z","uid":34889,"like":40,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"55ea48abdfa6f795f95d3b2e5ef409fb58211e9d","tid":1155784,"uid":34889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T07:28:07.000Z","msg":"係呀，好人好者睇殘體，唔屌得咩？<br />\n得，不過唔該你自問自己有冇貪平用淘寶買小米，<br />\n你有冇喺你朋友打錯字嘅時候糾正佢？<br />\n你有冇喺你能力/認知範圍內將蝗国拒於千里先<br />\n<br />\n大佬，你捍衛本土唔係話打撚沉個人就叫做到嘢，<br />\n達哥的確而家講嘢係就住就住，<br />\n但係你地矛頭係咪應該指住啲上強国飲喜茶、<br />\n睇支那劇嘅人先啱<br />\n<br />\n如果你真係一個自己做得咁足去對抗支共嘅人，<br />\n咁達哥真係抵俾你屌，但係比達哥更抵屌嘅人你地都唔好當睇唔到"},{"pid":"566afd0b96a46ff68f06aa192c3e2bb742ba42bd","tid":1155784,"uid":11173,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T07:41:08.000Z","msg":"都係果句，一大班欺善怕惡既偽善者<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e80fe74ef2b05e563e44f5b802284879bd1aef27","tid":1155784,"uid":182854,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T07:42:11.000Z","msg":"又係whataboutism<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90d60ad4b8beb350f1c78e3bea5ca6a172f75442","tid":1155784,"uid":34889,"like":2,"dislike":7,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"e80fe74ef2b05e563e44f5b802284879bd1aef27","tid":1155784,"uid":182854,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T07:42:11.000Z","msg":"又係whataboutism<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T07:53:14.000Z","msg":"用淘寶買国貨憑咩屌人，<br />\n藉呢個機會畀啲人反省下自己平時有幾反蝗反共，<br />\n唔係靠聲大大"},{"pid":"6b62419e7e7d9f801eb4170595df77c26cd4855b","tid":1155784,"uid":72645,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T08:15:41.000Z","msg":"點解要假設<br />\n反殘體嘅巴打一定有用過淘寶飲過喜茶<br />\n<br />\n咁你同嗰啲你哋所謂 盲反達哥嘅假設<br />\n揀殘體一定係奶共<br />\n<br />\n有咩分別？咪又係冇屈到有<br />\n你咪又係盲反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\